DiscountCodeGenerator.cartDiscountsDescr: Link these discount codes to one or multiple cart discounts.
DiscountCodeGenerator.cartDiscountsNote: Note: Cart Discounts are needed to Import the discount codes. Only the discounts with key and discount code as mandatory will be available.
DiscountCodeGenerator.cartPredicateDescr: When a condition is defined, the discount code can only be applied to carts that match this predicate (rule). Leave empty when discount code applies to all carts without restriction.
DiscountCodeGenerator.discountCodeFields: Use the fields to populate all codes with same attributes, leave empty to generate code with no attributes.
DiscountCodeGenerator.importInfo: Your file is being processed, it may take a few moments to complete depending on its size. You can check the progress and results in the Import logs.
DiscountCodeGenerator.keyDescription: Note: Keys are needed to Import the discount codes. They can either be generated randomly or be manually filled once the file is downloaded.
DiscountCodeGenerator.prefixRecommendati: We recommend using at least 13 characters for each code and a unique prefix for each batch to prevent duplicates (e.g., SUMMER26-00000).
DiscountCodeGenerator.previewRecommendat: We recommend using at least 10 characters for each code and a unique prefix for each batch to prevent duplicates (e.g., SUMMER26-00000).
DiscountCodeGenerator.previewTitle: {count} discount codes are ready to preview:
DiscountCodeGenerator.quantityDescriptio: The quantity of codes must be between 1 and 500,000. Note: If you plan to import codes later, the import limit is 200,000.
DiscountCodeGenerator.selectCartDiscount: Select one or more cart discounts
DiscountCodeGenerator.subtitle: Generate random discount codes using only uppercase letters and numbers
DiscountCodeGenerator.title: Discount Code Generator (Uppercase)
DiscountCodeGenerator.totalCharactersLab: Total number of characters for each code
DiscountCodeGenerator.uppercaseInfo: All generated codes will contain only uppercase letters (A-Z) and numbers (0-9). No lowercase letters will be used.
